    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slime Hero</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/0e1df6677360de783eb17d5ad330974f.poster.avif?t=1666004915\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/0e1df6677360de783eb17d5ad330974f.webm?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/0e1df6677360de783eb17d5ad330974f.mp4?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>史莱姆英雄是一款收集与战斗的游戏,你需要收集并组成你最爱的史莱姆战队去通过所有关卡,最后打败传说中的魔王.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/5d29e6d0fcdeae0d3bc40ab0c1f7b28b.poster.avif?t=1666004915\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/5d29e6d0fcdeae0d3bc40ab0c1f7b28b.webm?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/5d29e6d0fcdeae0d3bc40ab0c1f7b28b.mp4?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不管你的史莱姆战队有多强,你还是要小心闪避,身为队长的你,只要被打到血条归零,关卡就会失败,你的战队会保护你并自动攻击你的敌人们,收集并养成你的史莱姆英雄们,组成最强的史莱姆战队过关.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/83d4cb05f8bb84a7a406d412c6ab941b.poster.avif?t=1666004915\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/83d4cb05f8bb84a7a406d412c6ab941b.webm?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/83d4cb05f8bb84a7a406d412c6ab941b.mp4?t=1666004915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>史莱姆英雄里有超过50种的史莱姆可以收集,每个史莱姆英雄都有自己的独特攻击方式,也可以经过战斗养成后进化,你可以组成属于自己的史莱姆战队,希望你玩得愉快.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过50种史莱姆英雄等着被收集</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>用你最爱的史莱姆战队打败敌人</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>进化你最爱的史莱姆</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50种以上的攻击方式等着你探索</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>没有任何限制的自由组队</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4个完全不同的关卡可以探索</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3阶段不同难度等你挑战</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1个让人感到绝望的魔王等着你</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过10种不同的成就可以收集</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chill Game</h2>史莱姆英雄这款游戏会带给你放松休闲的游戏时光,带着你的史莱姆战队冒险战斗吧,每个关卡都有特别之处等着你去发掘.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏控制</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/064c0c25d97ae0e1d37ca2b3c0962352.avif?t=1666004915\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138400/extras/661ec63a36ad6a4ccaccba48cd957e9c.avif?t=1666004915\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
